{{flavour|Exhales a large cloud of fumes filled with the very essence of chaos.}}

'''Chaos Breath''' is a monster-only spell which emits a stream of [[Cloud#Seething chaos|seething chaos]] clouds, inflicting [[chaotic]] effects on anything that stays inside. On impact, it deals minor damage and causes a chaotic effect. It is subject to a [[Breath]] cooldown. 

